{"tid":224191,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"一入廁所 就要我幫佢汁番個頭（細膽咪入）","createTime":"2017-04-30T20:25:42.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-03T07:55:36.000Z","uid":89402,"like":24,"dislike":23,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"21475cd6701db83748be4aa6ad06314db53e1ae2","tid":224191,"uid":89402,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-30T20:25:42.000Z","msg":"夜更工廠撚<br />\n痴撚線 <br />\n己經都唔係第一次了<br />\n想痾篤尿姐<br />\n一入去諗住洗個面先<br />\n望住塊鏡 反射後面廁格有個影 （3格廁格）<br />\n中間個格閂左 左右兩格開左既 佢就飄左係中間閂左門個隔<br />\n仆你個街 飄到咁撚高都算<br />\n仲要頭都無個<br />\n個下心都離一離 之後心呼吸左陣 但手都係有少少震<br />\n沉住氣問佢 有咩幫到你？<br />\n好撚串 伸隻手出黎指住左手面個廁格個馬桶<br />\n個馬桶蓋上左既 <br />\n係 我係己經麻木左<br />\n我行過去打開個蓋 <br />\n係 係人頭 男人 白到無血色 眼反白 望都唔想望<br />\n眼未埋一條線咁架啦 一野捉住佢啲頭髮<br />\n嗱嗱臨一野掉落佢個手度<br />\n手都唔洗算 尿己經縮番上腸咁滯<br />\n沖番出去扮無野<br />\n係 係己經麻木左了<br />\n唔知由幾時開始..."},{"pid":"686336017244c9d70b1214b5db101eb02c583abd","tid":224191,"uid":27770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-30T20:27:22.000Z","msg":"真人真事？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/32.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b680a1a17dc34c1163ec4cc48dca5deccea3cf3","tid":224191,"uid":21392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-30T20:28:15.000Z","msg":"仲以為有圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b45e2bf4326056c191d0c1e121998b6bcb3a06e1","tid":224191,"uid":89402,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-30T20:30:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>真人真事？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/32.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n啱啱既事 <br />\n個阿頭問我做咩個人呆左咁多？<br />\n我笑笑口話無野 番夜實眼訓架啦"},{"pid":"443b3e059ee66cc09436d2b4a60d504f228db37e","tid":224191,"uid":24128,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-30T20:30:58.000Z","msg":"嚇撚死咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1deae9d646fc8cc98e9ad25e062f03e5cc81deff","tid":224191,"uid":89402,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-30T20:31:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>仲以為有圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我睇到既未必你地睇到<br />\n更何況用手機影到既話<br />\n可能我己經開唔到呢個post"},{"pid":"f7a80774a7950f2d700b430d662eec3545a0b71e","tid":224191,"uid":103212,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-30T20:31:37.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"21589006ce04bee5c9fdc638105b2966f2745027","tid":224191,"uid":103212,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-30T20:32:09.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e0386d419d35343ad07f872d04074ff402c96ac4","tid":224191,"uid":74851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-30T20:33:37.000Z","msg":"屌好撚驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"43181b3690156dee72c52abfd350935f1efd6b2a","tid":224191,"uid":78769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-30T20:34:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"840f8857f583c37b3b455d85672cc70b7d44f584","tid":224191,"uid":89402,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-30T20:38:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>下次佢再係咁 你拎*起*佢個頭一野窩利抽射 再大喝一聲<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">屌你老母自己執</span></blockquote></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n唔係下下都見到呢啲"},{"pid":"11dece65b67263a24b918b32f2e0d7d9f0979225","tid":224191,"uid":110380,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-30T20:38:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>下次佢再係咁 你拎*起*佢個頭一野窩利抽射 再大喝一聲<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">屌你老母自己執</span></blockquote></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n唔係下下都見到呢啲</blockquote><br />\n佢老母出埋黎 咁你點做"},{"pid":"db514b6b3d89e1ce1008bb2fce34cab9290543b9","tid":224191,"uid":15921,"like":0,"disli