"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n一陣得閒分享下又要開工了<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d84b1c37db1e19d4c352cff9eaabcf3dea56d61c","tid":224191,"uid":33491,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-30T21:03:22.000Z","msg":"執呀<br />\n汁你老母咩"},{"pid":"3ff5e6ad83914cf995aae5847e72ba58335defd2","tid":224191,"uid":89402,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-30T21:03:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>下次佢再係咁 你拎*起*佢個頭一野窩利抽射 再大喝一聲<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">屌你老母自己執</span></blockquote></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n唔係下下都見到呢啲</blockquote><br />\n佢老母出埋黎 咁你點做</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n即刻講對唔住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  你想無命?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n屌你啦 我幫佢汁番己經係因為我好心咋<br />\n我出於好意所以先問佢有咩幫到佢<br />\n唔係既話之後纏住我就仲煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"539a64faf0566cabbd4ab8446ff7fcdf7ca081d7","tid":224191,"uid":37318,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-30T21:12:54.000Z","msg":"邊間工廠？"},{"pid":"f3e7c641a2f0b1c32ead840e91a32edd65856b8c","tid":224191,"uid":26773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-30T21:13:18.000Z","msg":"回魂夜"},{"pid":"1a4bb35ea5ee45598b363ce091229d757a9e06ca","tid":224191,"uid":89402,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-30T21:20:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>邊間工廠？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n大埔區 唔講邊間啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"927ba7b773323f535955e4e48961f29f8db8cfaa","tid":224191,"uid":89402,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-30T21:21:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>回魂夜</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n應該死左好耐 邊得黎仲回魂"},{"pid":"b990da74ce02cb16b41b1fb6d25a8597be6181c5","tid":224191,"uid":52571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-30T21:21:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>