lown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n港島個頭啦總之"},{"pid":"d2512742689cc6fdb311fd500bc91d05d63a0231","tid":224191,"uid":15949,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T03:19:51.000Z","msg":"LM"},{"pid":"8d7c8f41777238375acfd0de07425438f1533076","tid":224191,"uid":89402,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T03:20:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>樓主點解由做不孝子開始就開左眼咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n報應掛<br />\n其實未睇到前覺得個味野只係另一種生物 <br />\n存在係我地睇唔到既空間<br />\n睇到之後 慣左 其實又好似無乜野"},{"pid":"a3a0a7bec8ac6599857fccc6d68b067653976ef1","tid":224191,"uid":107909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T03:21:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>碧唔可以講間戲院係邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n碧乜柒？</blockquote><br />\n咪改左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ffb86a15f01625e05102b198ed384ab6f7934f1","tid":224191,"uid":89402,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T03:24:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>碧唔可以講間戲院係邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n碧乜柒？</blockquote><br />\n咪改左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你打錯字啲人係會鬧番個樓主架 所以我先至咁執著<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c6600fa1606fcb18a61ee01aad452e6fcfe1a0fd","tid":224191,"uid":17111,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T03:26:12.000Z","msg":"所以考順親人 拜山真係好重要<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"93b94943a88f2a240b952914e7afd91fb42956b6","tid":224191,"uid":30778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T03:31:32.000Z","msg":"其實係咪你唔搞佢地，佢地就唔會搞返你架？<br />\n啲電影成日講到佢地一黎就會攞你命咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8bfedcce0b5feaedd2d27eaeed5e45c8cfad7afa","tid":224191,"uid":20622,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T03:34:17.000Z","msg":"原來故黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea95ff622f987e21bd1d065bdab8d92aa09ef8f4","tid":224191,"uid":20622,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T03:35:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實係咪你唔搞佢地，佢地就唔會搞返你架？<br />\n啲電影成日講到佢地一黎就會攞你命咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n啊通成套電影講大家唔搞大家咩"},{"pid":"82decd97775e2d01e2d1e53820e707af8001225c","tid":224191,"uid":20622,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T03:35:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>其實係咪你唔搞佢地，佢地就唔會搞返你架？<br />\n啲電影成日講到佢地一黎就會攞你命咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔通成套電影講大家唔搞大家咩</blockquote>"},{"pid":"9c0d9658148361ca8e23bb23c0673a819f80245c","tid":224191,"uid":8103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T03:45:11.000Z","msg":"分唔到係故定真人真事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  仲有冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"545121bcec1d7a2c083443bac3e5e7c95d755858","tid":224191,"uid":44243,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T03:48:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>樓主係精神病患者<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n正常回覆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"648ffe50fc7062e80d28db63cc92d873a77c5a29","tid":224191,"uid":76845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T03:55:36.000Z","msg":"好睇，繼續"},{"pid":"ce556d8da6c7575d52581a4947e48fc0994835c7","tid":224191,"uid":111002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T03:56:30.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"744a6f93a0effff3be733fa697d2d3e99ee67f8d","tid":224191,"uid":85313,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T03:57:22.000Z","msg":"有feel,繼續講多啲"},{"pid":"521db548d720898b4c767e756532c5b3525c112a","tid":224191,"uid":4219,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T04:00:07.000Z","msg":"想知多d more<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}